content: been feelin pretty down today but have you seen how pretty some of these birds out here are

Don’t be down friend! There is lots to smile about!
1. Those pretty birds (of course)
2. You’re a talented artist & on the road to success
3. You’re a great friend to all
4. You make a great horchata latte
5. The sun is shining and it’s warm out
6. Most important, Gods got you
